&gt;&gt; On Tue, Dec 16, 2025 at 1:38 AM Mike Taylor &lt;&lt;a href="/cdn-cgi/l/email-protection" class="__cf_email__" data-cfemail="036e6a686677622d2d2d43606b716c6e6a766e2d6c7164"&gt;[email&#160;protected]&lt;/a&gt;&gt; 
