*TL;DR:* Save the date and join us on *April 20-21, 2026* for BlinkOn 21 in
Redmond, WA, USA!&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;pre&gt;

Hi everyone,

We’re happy to announce that BlinkOn 21 will be hosted by Microsoft in
April 2026 in Redmond, WA.
Our intention with BlinkOn 21 is to continue what we did with BlinkOn 20
and continue down the path of BlinkOn of old where we could have multiple
tracks of smaller presentations with less emphasis on a polished
presentation.

*Save the Date!*
*What:* Combination of live and recorded sessions, including keynotes,
lightning talks, breakout talks, and social events
*When:* April 20-21, 2026
*Where:* Redmond, WA, USA

Registration will open soon, but please hold off on booking travel until
registration is confirmed. Stay tuned for more details (including travel)
in the coming weeks. Until then, if you have any questions or concerns,
don't hesitate to email us at &lt;a href="/cdn-cgi/l/email-protection" class="__cf_email__" data-cfemail="3a585653541414147a5952485557534f571455485d"&gt;[email&#160;protected]&lt;/a&gt;.

With gratitude,
BlinkOn Planning Committee

