*Reason this experiment is being extended* &lt;/pre&gt;&lt;tt&gt;A major partner is about to start a large-scale experiment. We believe &lt;/tt&gt;&lt;tt&gt;that extending the trial to cover their experiment window is crucial, &lt;/tt&gt;&lt;tt&gt;as it will provide us with essential performance metrics and stability &lt;/tt&gt;&lt;tt&gt;data at scale. This extension will prevent any service disruption for &lt;/tt&gt;&lt;tt&gt;the partner and ensure we have sufficient evidence to support the &lt;/tt&gt;&lt;tt&gt;final launch. &lt;/tt&gt;&lt;pre style="margin: 0em;"&gt;
