&lt;h1&gt;
&lt;span class="subject"&gt;&lt;a href="/search?l=blink-dev@chromium.org&amp;q=subject:%22%5C%5Bblink%5C-dev%5C%5D+Intent+to+Ship%5C%3A+Local+Network+Access+split+permissions%22&amp;o=newest" rel="nofollow"&gt;&lt;span itemprop="name"&gt;[blink-dev] Intent to Ship: Local Network Access split permissions&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/h1&gt;
&lt;p class="darkgray font13"&gt;
&lt;span class="sender pipe"&gt;&lt;a href="/search?l=blink-dev@chromium.org&amp;q=from:%22Hubert+Chao%22" rel="nofollow"&gt;&lt;span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Person"&gt;&lt;span itemprop="name"&gt;Hubert Chao&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;span class="date"&gt;&lt;a href="/search?l=blink-dev@chromium.org&amp;q=date:20260108" rel="nofollow"&gt;Thu, 08 Jan 2026 12:24:04 -0800&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div itemprop="articleBody" class="msgBody"&gt;

&lt;pre&gt;*Contact emails*
&lt;a href="/cdn-cgi/l/email-protection" class="__cf_email__" data-cfemail="7018135e5e5e301318021f1d19051d5e1f0217"&gt;[email&#160;protected]&lt;/a&gt;,  &lt;a href="/cdn-cgi/l/email-protection" class="__cf_email__" data-cfemail="7417001c5a5a5a34171c061b191d01195a1b0613"&gt;[email&#160;protected]&lt;/a&gt; &lt;&lt;a href="/cdn-cgi/l/email-protection" class="__cf_email__" data-cfemail="18707b363636587b706a7775716d7536776a7f"&gt;[email&#160;protected]&lt;/a&gt;&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;pre&gt;

*Summary*
This is an enhancement to the Local Network Access(LNA) restrictions, where
we split the permission required from one Local Network Access permission,
into 2 separate permissions.

Old permission name:
local-network-access

New Permission names:
local-network (for LNA requests to IPs in the local address space)
loopback-network (for LNA requests to IPs in the loopback address space)

The old permission names are kept as an alias and should continue to work
for permissions.query and Permissions Policy for the foreseeable future.

See &lt;a  rel="nofollow" href="https://chromestatus.com/feature/5152728072060928"&gt;https://chromestatus.com/feature/5152728072060928&lt;/a&gt; for an overview of
LNA;
&lt;a  rel="nofollow" href="https://groups.google.com/a/chromium.org/g/blink-dev/c/cwu_RUmBpzY/m/JWenvGViCAAJ"&gt;https://groups.google.com/a/chromium.org/g/blink-dev/c/cwu_RUmBpzY/m/JWenvGViCAAJ&lt;/a&gt;
for the original LNA I2S, and
&lt;a  rel="nofollow" href="https://github.com/WICG/local-network-access/issues/17"&gt;https://github.com/WICG/local-network-access/issues/17&lt;/a&gt; for a discussion of
splitting the permission and the naming of the new permissions.

*Blink component*
Blink &gt; SecurityFeature &gt; LocalNetworkAccess
