The HTTP header implementation was done using a network delegate helper:
&lt;a  rel="nofollow" href="https://github.com/brave/brave-core/blob/master/browser/net/global_privacy_control_network_delegate_helper.cc"&gt;https://github.com/brave/brave-core/blob/master/browser/net/global_privacy_control_network_delegate_helper.cc&lt;/a&gt;.
This was all back in 2020 though so probable that best practices
have changed.



