&gt;&gt; &lt;a href="/cdn-cgi/l/email-protection" class="__cf_email__" data-cfemail="9efcf2f7f0f5b3fafbe8defdf6ecf1f3f7ebf3b0f1ecf9"&gt;[email&#160;protected]&lt;/a&gt;&gt; wrote:
