&lt;pre&gt;Thank you for raising this issue.

We've already reached out to folks representing 99% of the remaining Shared
Storage API calls, and will reach out to the rest soon. We're confident
that we can remove this API by the proposed milestone with minimal user
breakage or utility loss.&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;pre&gt;

